title: DGK - UNITED COLORS OF DGK x APB - COMMERCIAL
description: DGK teamed up with Hawaii's APB skate shop for this new United Colors collaboration. In honor of the occasion we took DGK AM and Hawaii native Shmatty Chaffin to the beach for a relaxing day that ended with a little twist - it was all a dream!
